WizMySQLAdmin - Changelog
=========================

WizMySQLAdmin 0.11.4
--------------------
- fixed a bug when "order by" is specified into the query textbox (Thanks to Sarah Zelechoski for bug report)
- change ascending/descendig order clicking on the column header in browsing table mode


WizMySQLAdmin 0.11.3
--------------------
- fixed a bug when database/tables/fields contains hypens (Thanks to Rob Parker for bug report)
- fixed other little flaws


WizMySQLAdmin 0.11.2
--------------------
- code improvement (Thanks to Max Faber)


WizMySQLAdmin 0.11.1
--------------------
- fixed a bug executing queries with special charater "$" (thanks to Tomek Klimczak for bug report)
- fixed a bug executing queries with special charater ";" (thanks to Bob for bug report)
- improved portability (thanks to Bruce Painter for report)
- some other minor bug fixes and improvements


WizMySQLAdmin 0.10.8
--------------------
- fixed a bug removing field content (thanks to Kees Serier for bug report)
- added support for sorting columns during browsing


WizMySQLAdmin 0.10.6
--------------------
- fixed a bug into table properties (thanks to Kees Serier for bug report)


WizMySQLAdmin 0.10.5
--------------------
- added support for enum and set types
- added support for alter table stucture
- added indexes management
- fixed bug dropping tables and databases (thanks to anonymous for bug report)
- fixed bug inserting record into table
- greatly improved select and free query execution, also cleaning redundant code (op=3 has been removed, merged with op=4)
- removed SELECT form from left toolbar if database has no tables
- improved output readability in some function (ie: browse, insert/edit)
- a lot of minor enhancements and bugfixes


WizMySQLAdmin 0.9.0
-------------------
- fixed manual SELECT query execution: now it doesn't report if the query has success but the query result
- other minor bugfixes


WizMySQLAdmin 0.8.9
-------------------
- fixed a problem with GNU GPL license compliance


WizMySQLAdmin 0.8.8
-------------------
- added "query from file" function
- added "optimize table" function
- fixed error when no table selected


WizMySQLAdmin 0.8.6
-------------------
- added support for multiple databases
- added support for multiple tables
- added support for table creation
- a lot of other minor feature improvements
- bugfixes
- graphic design improved


WizMySQLAdmin 0.6.4
-------------------
Initial public release
